data.description: This 3 bed, 2 bath residence offers spacious living areas, a charming shed, and a delightful covered patio. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere that flows throughout the home. The generous-sized rooms provide ample space for all your needs. One of the highlights of this property is the nice shed, which offers additional storage space for your tools, equipment, or hobbies. Step outside onto the inviting covered patio, where you can relax and enjoy the beauty of the outdoors.
